<h1>More data so you can Kick Safer.</h1>
	<p>
Our goal is to empower everyone who uses the Kickstarter platform. We're not trying to dissuade competitive decision making. The great part about Kickstarter is that projects succeed entirely on the signals they send to potential backers. It's all up to the community to determine which projects live or die.
</p>
<div class="accordian" id="accordian2">
	<div class="accordian-group">
		<div class="accordian-heading">
