</div>

<p> So whether you're trying to maximize your potential reward, sorting out if a creator's claim is legitimate, or simply looking for another way to sift through the many great projects on the site, you should check out the advice of our review team. We're always looking to improve and welcome any feedback to make our data even more useful! Our figurative door is always open.</p>
<p>-Tristan
